  "data": {
    "title": "Pipedrive's New AI Features Transform How Sales Teams Close Deals",
    "excerpt": "Pipedrive just rolled out AI-powered tools that make pipeline management effortless. Discover what's new and why 100K+ teams swear by this CRM.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
        "url": "https://tonyciencia.com/blog/pipedrive-new-features.jpg",
        "alt": "Pipedrive's New AI Features Transform How Sales Teams Close Deals",
        "filename": "pipedrive-new-features.jpg"
      }
    },
    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've tested a lot of CRMs over the years. Some feel like they were designed by engineers who've never made a cold call. Others try so hard to be \"everything\" that they become a cluttered mess nobody on the team actually wants to use.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then there's Pipedrive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pipedrive has always been the CRM that salespeople actually enjoy using. The drag-and-drop pipeline, the visual deal tracking, the \"get out of my way so I can sell\" philosophy — it's been a favorite for over 100,000 companies for good reason.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "But lately, they've made some serious upgrades. We're talking built-in AI, smarter reporting, and automation that genuinely saves hours every week. If you haven't looked at Pipedrive recently, you're missing the best version yet.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let me walk you through what's changed, why it matters, and whether it's the right fit for your team.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "---",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Disclosure: This post contains affiliate links. If you sign up through our links, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.",
            "marks": []
