      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What's New in Pipedrive: AI and Smarter Workflows",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Pipedrive made the biggest leap. Their latest updates bring artificial intelligence directly into the daily workflow — not as a gimmick, but as a practical tool that helps reps close faster.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Report Creation",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Building reports used to mean exporting spreadsheets, wrestling with pivot tables, and praying the numbers matched. Now, Pipedrive lets you generate reports using plain text input or choose from pre-written prompts. Type something like \"show me deals won this quarter by rep\" and you get a clean, visual report in seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For sales managers, this is a game-changer. You spend less time building dashboards and more time coaching your team based on real data.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-Time Sales Feed",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pipedrive now includes a real-time sales feed — a smart, focused workspace where you can track follow-ups, spot overdue tasks, and catch new opportunities as they surface. It's like having a personal assistant who taps you on the shoulder whenever something needs attention.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "No more digging through your pipeline wondering, \"Did I follow up with that lead?\" The feed tells you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI Now Available on Every Plan",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's something worth noting: Pipedrive didn't gatekeep the AI features behind their most expensive tier. The Lite plan — their entry-level option at $14/seat/month (billed annually) — now includes AI-powered report creation and the real-time sales feed. Even small teams and solo reps get access to the smart stuff.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "That's a bold move, and it shows Pipedrive's commitment to making powerful tools accessible, not exclusive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
