        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Core Strengths That Make Pipedrive Stand Out",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The new AI features are exciting, but let's not forget why Pipedrive earned its reputation in the first place. These foundational strengths are what make the platform feel so intuitive day after day.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Visual Pipeline That Actually Makes Sense",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pipedrive's drag-and-drop pipeline is the centerpiece of the experience. You see every deal laid out in columns — stages like \"Initial Contact,\" \"Proposal Sent,\" \"Negotiation,\" \"Won.\" Drag a card from one stage to the next as the deal progresses.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "It sounds simple because it is. And that's the point. Your entire sales process fits on one screen. No clicking through menus. No wondering where a deal stands. You see it, you move it, you close it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automation That Feels Invisible",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Nobody got into sales to write follow-up reminder emails by hand. Pipedrive's automation engine handles the repetitive stuff — sending follow-ups, updating deal stages, assigning tasks — so reps spend their time on conversations, not data entry.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Growth plan ($39/seat/month billed annually) takes this further with automated email sequences and follow-up workflows. Set it once, and Pipedrive does the nudging for you.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Reporting That Managers Actually Use",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Beyond the new AI reports, Pipedrive's performance dashboards give you a clear picture of team activity, conversion rates, and revenue forecasts. The visual format means you can glance at a screen and know exactly where things stand — no spreadsheet gymnastics required.",
            "marks": []
          }
