      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your primary goal is closing deals — not managing projects, not running marketing campaigns, not building customer support queues — Pipedrive is laser-focused on that mission. It's a sales CRM built by people who understand the sales process. That focus shows in every feature.",
            "marks": []
