        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Pipedrive hits a sweet spot for growing companies. It's powerful enough to handle complex pipelines but simple enough that you won't need weeks of onboarding. Their personalized onboarding option (available even on the Lite plan) helps you get set up fast.",
            "marks": []
          }
