        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Getting the Most Out of Pipedrive",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "A few tips I've picked up from teams who love Pipedrive:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customize your pipeline stages.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Don't stick with the defaults. Rename stages to match your actual sales process. It makes the visual pipeline even more intuitive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use the AI reports weekly.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Set a recurring task to run your key reports every Monday. It takes 30 seconds and gives you a data-driven start to the week.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Automate your follow-ups first.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " If you only automate one thing, make it follow-up reminders. This alone prevents leads from going cold.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "4. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Connect your email and calendar.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Pipedrive logs emails and meetings automatically once connected. No manual entry needed.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "5. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Explore the integrations gallery.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " There are over 500 options. Chances are, at least five of your current tools have native Pipedrive integrations.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l5",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/pipedrive-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For more tips like these, we've put together a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "complete guide to Pipedrive best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l5"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Bottom Line: Should You Try Pipedrive?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here's my honest take: Pipedrive was already one of the best CRMs for sales teams before these AI updates. Now, with AI-powered reporting, real-time feeds, and smart automation available on every plan, it's even harder to argue against it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform is fast, visual, and built for people who sell. It doesn't try to be an all-in-one project management suite. It does sales CRM exceptionally well, and the new features make it smarter without making it complicated.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your team needs a CRM that people will actually use — not one that collects digital dust after onboarding — Pipedrive deserves a serious look.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l6",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://aff.trypipedrive.com/vyzzvh7thge6"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start your free 14-day Pipedrive trial here",
            "marks": [
              "l6"
